OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChristmas cutbacks cause   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fshock drop in shop sales   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Shop sales fell by record numbers both 
OL,6, in December and across the whole of    
OL,7, last year as consumers cut spending.   
OL,9,FRetail sales had been expected to rise 
OL,10,Flast month in what is a key season for 
OL,11,Fshops because of Christmas.            
OL,13,FHowever, the volume of goods people    
OL,14,Fbought in December fell by 1% from     
OL,15,FNovember, and by a record 5.8% compared
OL,16,Fwith December 2021.                    
OL,18,FThe Office for National Statistics     
OL,19,F(ONS) also confirmed retail sales for  
OL,20,Flast year recorded the worst-ever fall.
